00287 bool GCOSCHPDataAdapter::GetResequencingResults(FusionResequencingResults& result)
00288 {
00289         CResequencingResults* ps = 0;
00290         ps = gcosChp.GetResequencingResults();
00291         if (ps)
00292         {
00293                 int32_t sz = ps->GetCalledBasesSize();
00294                 for(int i = 0; i < sz; i++)
00295                 {
00296                         result.AddCalledBase(ps->GetCalledBase(i));
00297                 }
00298                 sz = ps->GetScoresSize();
00299                 for(int i = 0; i < sz; i++)
00300                 {
00301                         result.AddScore(ps->GetScore(i));
00302                 }
00303                 sz = ps->GetForceCallsSize();
00304                 for(int i = 0; i < sz; i++)
00305                 {
00306                         ForceCallType f = ps->GetForceCall(i);
00307                         FusionForceCallType fusionType(f.position, f.call, f.reason);
00308                         result.AddForceCall(fusionType);
00309                 }
00310                 sz = ps->GetOrigCallsSize();
00311                 for(int i = 0; i < sz; i++)
00312                 {
00313                         BaseCallType b = ps->GetOrigCall(i);
00314                         FusionBaseCallType fusionType(b.position, b.call);
00315                         result.AddOrigCall(fusionType);
00316                 }
00317 
00318                 return true;
00319         }
00320         return false;
